org.fujion.page

Class PageDefinitionCache

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.fujion.common.AbstractCache<String,PageDefinition>
      • org.fujion.page.PageDefinitionCache
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<PageDefinition>

    public class PageDefinitionCache
extends AbstractCache<String,PageDefinition>
    A cache of all compiled page definitions. If a requested page is not in the cache, it will be automatically compiled and added to the cache.
